ActCanada Wildlife Act
SubjectOrder Authorizing the Minister of Environment to enter into an Agreement with the Government of Yukon and Northwest Territories
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2023-0676 of June 23, 2023; and (2) authorizing the Minister to enter into an Agreement with the Government of Yukon and the Inuvialuit Regional Corporation, the Inuvialuit Game Council, the Aklavik Hunters and Trappers Committee, and the Aklavik Community regarding the long-term management of the Aullaviat/Anguniarvik Traditional Conservation Area.
